{"tid":180625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學運占立法院無罪 地院認「正當行使公民不服從」","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60d2076c555603717211df007cf01dfda51be923","tid":180625,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"〔記者張文川／台北報導〕2014年引爆太陽花學運的「318攻占立法院行動」，林飛帆、陳為廷、黃國昌等22名被起訴指控煽惑犯罪、妨害公務等罪的被告，今獲台北地院宣判全都無罪，北院發布的新聞稿已全文上網，內容指出主要判決理由，包括，「帆廷昌」等人沒有煽惑他人犯罪的客觀行為與主觀犯意，進入立法院並非「無故」，而是有「行使公民不服從」的正當理由，因此判無罪。<br />\n<br />\n台北地方法院新聞稿全文如下：<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIczANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=be79d5ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&h=474e98ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329</a>"}]}